While these crags are obviously some manner of dwelling, the method of entry is not as apparent. Many of the screams originate from somewhere within the structure.

The large, flat slab of polished stone set prominently in the face of the terran housing is scored with a variety of marks. Some is writing in the Giant language, while the vast majority seem to be a tally of victories, or simply boasting about something.

This rock face, though quite steep, has many crags and outcroppings that could be used to climb by a strong individual. Should you fall while climbing however only cold, unyielding stone awaits below...
